from a water fountain,

226
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:37,720
they're gonna get poisoned
from paint in their homes.

227
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:42,560
I like how that starts off
sounding reassuring,

228
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:44,640
